{"tid":1818912,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"將香港正苦司法不公總結, 然後發過去外國金融評級機構, 要求將香港評級降級","createTime":"2020-01-10T10:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T16:50:33.000Z","uid":76310,"like":173,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"553d62d61438f6000e48a264cd78e91fed38d06b","tid":1818912,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"將香港正苦司法不公總結, 然後發過去外國金融評級機構, 要求將香港評級降級<br />\n呢個係實在可行既方法<br />\n但唔知點解無人建議做或無人去做, 以我個人能力, 真係做唔到<br />\n呢個方法, 好過大家繼續不斷去遊行集會, 遊行集會, 正苦: Who cares?. 那怕700萬人上街都話你.<br />\n堵街, 只不過影響一會, 轉頭就變回現狀, 但手足所付既代價以年計. <br />\n那怕裝修1000藍店, 一切如常, 影響不大. 但手足所付代價太大了.<br />\n<br />\n中共最睇重香港幾個能力, 其中一個: 金融地位, 尤其集資能力, 包括發美元債, IPO上市. 影響到香港金融評級, 會大大影響香港集資能力. 這是一個大大軟肋<br />\n好多手足, 已經被捕, 被還押, 有小部份更加判刑了. 我知大家覺得好似做什麼都無用. 而事實, 大家做既野, 影響唔到中共最看重既野, 影響零售, 影響旅遊, 影響民生, 中共都不太理會<br />\n但影響香港集資功能, 最影響中共. 中共需要香港借錢來債冚債<br />\n<br />\n將香港正苦司法不公總結, 法制影響金融, 絕對有關係. 要求將香港評級降級<br />\n如果不將我們承受既種種不公變成實在戰果去將香港金融評級降級, 正苦繼續做衰野和清算, 正苦是沒有後果的"},{"pid":"05e97cafedbba3bfd1240b029e473983008ac6b0","tid":1818912,"uid":47208,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"寫得好<br />\n<br />\n有人做緊<br />\n但可以繼續加速去做<br />\n<br />\n其實香港呢半年已經降左2級"},{"pid":"c775296a43fa8c315217741838124d972069d876","tid":1818912,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959e07999ec66eeeb7ea7a0a3b1ad7966f69ea92","tid":1818912,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"做呢樣野, 好過幾百萬人再遊行<br />\n遊行集會可以保持運動動力, 難聽d, 但實在說, 遊行集會, 用途不大"},{"pid":"ce08cf6e8476ee5bd389d5161d05399d71ab32e6","tid":1818912,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n-----------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港獨立</span>   <span style=\"color: gold;\">唯一出路</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>WARS</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe77a38385a989fd0e80ac538013725bc433f9e","tid":1818912,"uid":83910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"司法制席暴力<br />\n用「時間」玩死人<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n選舉呈請等結果等到差唔多換屆<br />\n收押幾個月再審"},{"pid":"1a4b2b942bda55902a5d098589d07baab624513b","tid":1818912,"uid":269481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:36:11.000Z","msg":"暫時得Fitch肯降，另外更大間嘅S&amp;P同Moody都未肯做野......<br />\n如果可以令到呢兩間都肯降嘅話，香港同鄰國企業嘅借貸成本即時上升，個攬炒程度真係唔敢想像呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a8d5cf88f7ad654e0a5b3ea78c8a2819ae6164","tid":1818912,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"有咩渠道可以直接email過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da34930336f52ab170d9ce479b00e453ca73a2f9","tid":1818912,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"呢個方法又合法, 又和平, 又零風險, 但對中共港共影響好大"},{"pid":"509096d52e523bf3ff04e15d070bd6b0bf18d4e7","tid":1818912,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\